title: Washington Week with Gwen Ifill for Friday, March 7, 2014 480p
description:
Washington Week with Gwen Ifill for Friday, March 7, 2014

Description:
The U.S. is ramping up pressure on Russia to de-escalate the growing tensions in Ukraine by imposing sanctions and visa restrictions. NY Times' Peter Baker and LA Times' Doyle McManus report on the latest developments in the crisis. Plus, Republicans, including many 2016 presidential hopefuls, gathered at the annual Conservative Political Action Conference to hone their message and rally their base ahead of the 2014 midterm elections. CNN's Gloria Borger reports.
